    <title>MOD Capability Review and Action Plan 2011-12</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary/>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Today, 29 June, the Ministry of Defence has published a Capability Review and Action plan.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The review is based on a self assessment and focuses on the Department’s capability in three broad areas:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Leadership 
Strategy 
Delivery
The Capability Review has been developed through extensive evidence-gathering work. The Department has been subject to extensive review over the past two years.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Capability Action Plan is based on assessments made by these reviews, and captures the progress which has been made in implementing the changes.  It identifies where further improvements can be made and highlights the Department’s next steps these actions are embedded in the Department’s work to transform Defence.&lt;/p&gt;

